column10: Because most motorized vehicles headed east on Hermosa Drive turn left onto northbound Nutley Street, cyclists headed west on Hermosa either have to wait for the left turns to cease or use the cross walk, then cross back to westbound Hermosa. Ugh.
column34: Please rename to near hit, or endangerment, or motorized minefields, not near miss, because that's what it is
